  31,6,"Hino woodi e yim…ìe …ìen, soodiroowo mbelee…óe konngu…ói haa o majjira e laawol Alla ngol ko aldaa e ganndal, o jogitora (aayeeje) …óen jalnitgol. …ìeen …óon, hino woodani …ìe lepte koynooje."
  31,7,"Si aayeeje Amen …óen njanngaama e makko, o huccitira(runtora) townitaare, wa si tawii o nanaani …óe, wa si tawii ko pahu woni e noppi makko. weltanir-mo lepte mu'us…óe."
  31,8,"Pellet, …ìen goo≈ã…óin…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin, hino woodani …ìe Aljannaaji neema."
  31,9,"Ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe ton, …óuum ko fodoore Alla goongunde. Ko Ka≈ãko woni On pool…óo, √ëee√±…óo."
  31,10,"O tagirii kammuuji …óin ko aldaa e tugaale, …óe nji'oton; o wernii ka leydi pelle fii wota ndi dillidu e mon; o saaki e mayri kala ruugayngel. Min njippiniri ndiyam ka kammu, Min pu…óini e mayri kala nooneeji teddu…ói."
  31,11,""∆äuum …óoo ko tagoore Alla. Kollee Kam ko …ói (ndewoton …óin) ga Makko tagi?" Si ko woni, too√±…ìe …ìeen no e majjere …ìanngunde."